Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.345
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:08.920
SPEAKER: We are here
today with Dan Carlin.

00:00:08.920 --> 00:00:12.640
He is the host of two very
